{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript/lecture-working-with-data-types/how-does-the-typeof-operator-work-and-what-is-the-typeof-null-bug-in-javascript","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"lecture-working-with-data-types","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":[{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Operator <code>typeof</code> u JavaScript je jednostavan, ali moćan alat koji vam omogućava da vidite tip podataka varijable ili vrednosti. Uvek vraća niz karaktera koji pokazuje taj tip.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Istražite nekoliko primera:</p>","files":null},{"type":"interactiveEditor","contents":null,"files":[{"ext":"js","name":"script-1","contents":"let num = 42;\nconsole.log(typeof num); // \"number\"","contentsHtml":"<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let num = 42;\nconsole.log(typeof num); // \"number\"\n</code></pre>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>U ovom prvom primeru, kreirali smo varijablu nazvanu <code>num</code> i dodelili joj vrednost broja <code>42</code>. Kada koristite operator <code>typeof</code> na varijabli nazvanoj <code>num</code>, vraća niz karaktera <code>number</code>.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Evo još jednog primera korišćenja operatera <code>typeof</code> na varijabli nazvanoj <code>isUserLoggedIn</code>:</p>","files":null},{"type":"interactiveEditor","contents":null,"files":[{"ext":"js","name":"script-1","contents":"let isUserLoggedIn = true;\nconsole.log(typeof isUserLoggedIn); // \"boolean\"","contentsHtml":"<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let isUserLoggedIn = true;\nconsole.log(typeof isUserLoggedIn); // \"boolean\"\n</code></pre>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Kada koristite operator <code>typeof</code> na varijabli <code>isUserLoggedIn</code>, vraća niz znakova <code>boolean</code> jer je toj varijabli dodata vrednost tačno ili netačno <code>true</code>.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Korišćenje operatera <code>typeof</code> može biti korisno posebno kada tražite greške ili pokušavate da razumete kakve podatke koristite u svom kodu.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Međutim, postoji veoma poznata greška u JavaScript kada je reč o pitanju <code>null</code>.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Pogledajmo primer:</p>","files":null},{"type":"interactiveEditor","contents":null,"files":[{"ext":"js","name":"script-1","contents":"let exampleVariable = null;\nconsole.log(typeof exampleVariable); // \"object\"","contentsHtml":"<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let exampleVariable = null;\nconsole.log(typeof exampleVariable); // \"object\"\n</code></pre>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>U ovom primeru, imamo varijablu nazvanu <code>exampleVariable</code> i dodelili smo joj vrednost <code>null</code>. Ali kada koristimo operator <code>typeof</code>, vraća niz karaktera <code>object</code>.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Ovo se smatra greškom u JavaScript, koja postoji od samog početka. Uzrok ovog ponašanja leži u tome kako JavaScript je prvobitno kreirano.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Kada je jezik prvi put implementiran, vrednosti kao što su <code>null</code> bile predstavljene kao specifičan tip objekta, i uzrokujući ove nepredvidive rezultate.</p>","files":null},{"type":"paragraph","contents":"<p>Nažalost, ovo je postalo deo jezika, i iako je zbunjujuće/konfuzno, to je nešto što ćete morati da uzmete u obzir.</p>","files":null}],"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript/lecture-working-with-data-types/how-does-the-typeof-operator-work-and-what-is-the-typeof-null-bug-in-javascript"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Operator <code>typeof</code> šta vraća kada ga koristite u nizu znakova u JavaScript?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>\"string\"</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>\"text\"</code></p>","feedback":"<p>Zamislite rezultate kada gledate tip <code>\"Hello\"</code>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>\"character\"</code></p>","feedback":"<p>Zamislite rezultate kada pregledate tip <code>\"Hello\"</code>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>\"object\"</code></p>","feedback":"<p>Zamislite rezultate kada pregledate tip <code>\"Hello\"</code>.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1},{"text":"<p>Zašto <code>typeof null</code> se smatra greškom u JavaScript?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Obnavlja <code>\"null\"</code> umesto <code>\"undefined\"</code>.</p>","feedback":"<p>Zapamti nepouzdano ponašanje kada gledaš vrstu <code>null</code>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Vraća <code>\"object\"</code> umesto <code>\"null\"</code>.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ne radiš na <code>null</code>.</p>","feedback":"<p>Setite se nepouzdane prirode kada gledate vrstu <code>null</code>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Vraća grešku.</p>","feedback":"<p>Zapamti nepouzdano ponašanje kada gledaš vrstu <code>null</code>.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2},{"text":"<p>Operator <code>typeof</code> šta vraća kada ga koristiš na broj u JavaScript?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>\"number\"</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>\"integer\"</code></p>","feedback":"<p>Razmislite o tipu koji vraća <code>typeof</code> za cijele brojeve i decimalne brojeve.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>\"numeric\"</code></p>","feedback":"<p>Razmislite o tipu koji se vraća sa <code>typeof</code> za cele brojeve i decimalne brojeve.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>\"float\"</code></p>","feedback":"<p>Razmislite o tipu koji se vraća sa <code>typeof</code> za celobrojne i decimalne brojeve.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript","tests":[],"title":"Kako radi `typeof` operator, i kakav je problem sa `typeof null` u JavaScriptu?","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript/#lecture-working-with-data-types","dashedName":"how-does-the-typeof-operator-work-and-what-is-the-typeof-null-bug-in-javascript","certification":"introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"lecture-working-with-data-types","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript/review-javascript-variables-and-data-types/review-javascript-variables-and-data-types","prevChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript/lecture-working-with-data-types/what-is-dynamic-typing-in-javascript-and-how-does-it-differ-from-statically-typed-languages","id":"6732518a8627876f4fcd18a4","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/introduction-to-variables-and-strings-in-javascript/lecture-working-with-data-types/how-does-the-typeof-operator-work-and-what-is-the-typeof-null-bug-in-javascript"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}